%p <strong>Update:</strong> I've been carrying this as my EDC for a few weeks now and I must say that I quite like it so far! The handle fits surprisingly well in the hand in all the relevant grip positions. Right now the blade has a bit too much belly, which stops you from easily using the point of the knife at a natural angle (like you would with an exacto).

%p I'm planning to make another prototype soon with a thinner blade, and a different blade profile. Stay tuned!